ns causes fuzziness in reasoning and vagueness in communication\nthat can be represented by some suitable classifications connected by some\nchannels. This new framework like a network framework can provide a scalable\nand open framework to cover different models based on a relativistic notion of\ntruth.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 5 Jun 2022 23:03:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-07"}
