e experiments across two\nbenchmark datasets and different unlabeled settings show that ACTION\nsignificantly outperforms the current state-of-the-art semi-supervised methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jun 2022 01:30:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Mar 2023 16:08:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 7 Mar 2023 02:14:39 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 10 Mar 2023 20:00:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-14"}
