ets generated by their friends. We\nanalysed the correlation for each ego network layer identified in Twitter,\ndiscovering their role in the diffusion of information.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jun 2022 08:31:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-07"}
