ervation law can be effective simultaneously.\nBut the charge conservation law and mass conservation law are unable to be\nvalid simultaneously, in the strict sense. It is beneficial to further\nunderstand the laws of conservation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jun 2022 04:12:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-16"}
